<hymn_number>254</hymn_number>
<title>Vawnsen Deihum</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chung Pathien vangsakna go thil
 Vawnsen deihum kei di'n tuoilo pak
 Muh loh laigil a damtui bang vung
 Vawnsen pallai kei di'n a hung vul

[V2]
 Pak bang chawi ka, kei ngaih ding dieng
 Chang bang damin suihlung pil hen
 Sakmel eta pawm chim loh vawnsen

[V3]
 2. Laigil vangsakna go thilpha
 Tuona chung Pathien thimthu tiemsa
 Kei din vawn dawng a hung pak san sel
 Sakmel deihum tuoisen chul mawh hen.

[V4]
 3. Chung Pathien vang gobang channa,
 Vawnsen pallai zatam suihlung nem pen
 Zuo chung Pathien, Na banzal nuoiah,
 Ka hun piei damsung Nang nasem ding.</lyrics>
</song>